{"tid":2011371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Twitter戰線】每日五分鐘打Twitter戰線教學","createTime":"2020-05-11T03:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T07:30:39.000Z","uid":341993,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3ebad759dc843e79e3bddc93bbfe82f74ec1603e","tid":2011371,"uid":341993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T03:10:36.000Z","msg":"唔想再見到直播淨係可以好嬲好嬲？<br />\n<br />\n好想煲大粒核彈？<br />\n<br />\n好想外國出手幫我地？<br />\n<br />\n唔知twitter戰線要從何入手？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以今日小弟就教大家點樣打最基本嘅twitter戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先我地要follow唔同嘅page<br />\n<br />\n然後每日花五分鐘開twitter出嚟retweet&amp;like<br />\n<br />\n咁就完成任務架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要follow哂啲page，以後一開twitter就可以啪啪啪咁like同retweet哂所有post喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗再辛苦手足整合幾廿個post<br />\n<br />\n唔洗再等bot餵到埋口<br />\n<br />\n想煲大邊粒核彈就煲大邊粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁低成本高回報嘅野，唔係唔做呀？<br />\n<br />\n最後整合左幾個twitter page比大家follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，歡迎各位手足喺樓下補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">周庭</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchowtingagnes&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=f9120aa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Gphone</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=c1b161d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">毛EE</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ClaudiaMCMo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FClaudiaMCMo&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=28ab36e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ClaudiaMCMo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">張崑陽</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SunnyCheungky\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSunnyCheungky&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=bd23f3c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SunnyCheungky</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Rubio</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=b2417896\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Solomon</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=fd4ff151\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒巴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=ef93997c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Benedict Rogers</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/benedictrogers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=1f029a13\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/bene